<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sa_pattern"><sa_pattern action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><ci_type>cmdb_ci_appl_generic</ci_type><cpattern_type>2</cpattern_type><description/><directory>false</directory><enforce_proc_classy>false</enforce_proc_classy><invoke_per_account>false</invoke_per_account><metadata_id>6642eb761b263950ed78dd3cdc4bcb9e</metadata_id><name>Extra GCP Resources</name><ndl>library {
	name = "Extra GCP Resources"
	id = "6642eb761b263950ed78dd3cdc4bcb9e"
	description = "Extra GCP Resources"
	step {
		name = "Load Balancer Library"
		ref {refid = "1ef51f3e1ba23950ed78dd3cdc4bcbcd"}
	}
	step {
		name = "Storage Bucket Library"
		ref {refid = "5e8753721be23950ed78dd3cdc4bcb47"}
	}
	step {
		name = "Pub Sub Library"
		ref {refid = "b75993361be23950ed78dd3cdc4bcbab"}
	}
	step {
		name = "Cloud Function Library"
		ref {refid = "e47997361be23950ed78dd3cdc4bcb28"}
	}
	step {
		name = "Build Relationship between Service Account and Resource"
		if {
			condition = is_not_empty {get_attr {"cmdb_ci_cmp_resource[1].name"}}
			on_true = relation_reference {
				table1_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
				key1_name = "category"
				table2_name = "cmdb_ci_cloud_service_account"
				key2_name = "account_id"
				result_table_name = "cmp_to_csa"
				unmatched_lines = remove
				relation_type = "Hosted on::Hosts"
				ref_direction = parentToChild
				ref_field_name = ""
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Build Relationship between Datacenter and Resource"
		if {
			condition = is_not_empty {get_attr {"cmdb_ci_cmp_resource[1].name"}}
			on_true = relation_reference {
				table1_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
				key1_name = "category"
				table2_name = "cmdb_ci_google_datacenter"
				key2_name = "name"
				result_table_name = "cmp_to_dc"
				unmatched_lines = remove
				relation_type = "Hosted on::Hosts"
				ref_direction = parentToChild
				ref_field_name = ""
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Create Key Value Reference"
		if {
			condition = is_not_empty {get_attr {"cmdb_key_value"}}
			on_true = relation_reference {
				table1_name = "cmdb_key_value"
				key1_name = "configuration_item"
				table2_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
				key2_name = "object_id"
				result_table_name = "label_to_resource"
				unmatched_lines = remove
				ref_direction = parentToChild
				ref_field_name = "configuration_item"
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
}

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sa_pattern"><sa_pattern action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><ci_type>cmdb_ci_appl_generic</ci_type><cpattern_type>2</cpattern_type><description/><directory>false</directory><enforce_proc_classy>false</enforce_proc_classy><invoke_per_account>false</invoke_per_account><metadata_id>5e8753721be23950ed78dd3cdc4bcb47</metadata_id><name>Storage Buckets GCP</name><ndl>library {
	name = "Storage Buckets GCP"
	id = "5e8753721be23950ed78dd3cdc4bcb47"
	description = "null"
	step {
		name = "Storage Bucket API Call"
		custom_operation {
			attributes {
				attribute {
					name = "url"
					value = concat {
						"https://storage.googleapis.com/storage/v1/b?project="
						get_attr {"cloud_account_id"}
					}
				}
				attribute {
					name = "method"
					value = "GET"
				}
				attribute {
					name = "body"
					value = ""
				}
				attribute {
					name = "headers"
					value = ""
				}
				attribute {
					name = "formatted"
					value = "true"
				}
				attribute {
					name = "arrayName"
					value = "storage_bucket_response"
				}
			}
			sys_id_op = "a6e5288173b363008c51d6dcb7f6a75e"
			to_var_names = "SystemVariable"
			parsing_strategy = empty_strategy {}
			if_not_found_do = nop {}
			is_paginated = 0
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse API Call"
		if {
			condition = is_not_empty {get_attr {"storage_bucket_response"}}
			on_true = custom_operation {
				attributes {
					attribute {
						name = "source"
						value = "storage_bucket_response"
					}
					attribute {
						name = "source_column"
						value = ""
					}
					attribute {
						name = "table_name"
						value = "storage_bucket"
					}
					attribute {
						name = "target_columns"
						value = "name:items.name,category:items.location"
					}
				}
				sys_id_op = "eb6ef2e353a533003e76ddeeff7b124d"
				to_var_names = "SystemVariable"
				parsing_strategy = empty_strategy {}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				is_paginated = 0
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse Storage bucket table"
		transform {
			src_table_name = "storage_bucket"
			target_table_name = "storage_bucket"
			operation {
				set_field {
					field_name = "name"
					value = get_attr {"storage_bucket[].name"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "object_id"
					value = get_attr {"storage_bucket[].name"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "category"
					value = eval {"javascript: var getRegion = ${storage_bucket[].category};rtrn  = getRegion.toLowerCase();if(rtrn == \"us\"){   rtrn = ${cloud_account_id};	 rtrn;}else{rtrn;}"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "resource_type"
					value = "storage.v1.bucket"
				}
			}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Move into cmdb_ci_cmp_resource Table"
		union {
			table1_name = "storage_bucket"
			table2_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
			result_table_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse Tags"
		set_attr {
			"tmp"
			eval {"javascript: var ArrayList = Packages.java.util.ArrayList;
var HashMap = Packages.java.util.HashMap;

// Create the target table
var storageBucketLabels = new ArrayList();
CTX.setAttribute('storage_buckets_labels', storageBucketLabels);

// Iterate over the response table
var response = CTX.getAttribute('storage_bucket_response');
var responseIter = response.iterator();

while (responseIter.hasNext()) {  
   var line = responseIter.next();
   var storageBucketObj = JSON.parse(line);
   for (var storageBucketIdx in storageBucketObj.items) {
      var storageBucket = storageBucketObj.items[storageBucketIdx];
      // Iterate over labels
      if (!storageBucket.labels)
         continue;
      
      for (var key in storageBucket.labels) {
	        // Create new row in the target object
          var storageBucketRow = new HashMap();
          storageBucketRow.put('configuration_item',storageBucket.id);
          storageBucketRow.put('key',key);
          storageBucketRow.put('value',storageBucket.labels[key]);
          storageBucketRow.put('sys_class_name','u_cmdb_ci_gcp_storage_bucket');
          storageBucketLabels.add(storageBucketRow);
      }
   }
}

rtrn = 'success'"}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Put Into Key Value Table"
		union {
			table1_name = "storage_buckets_labels"
			table2_name = "cmdb_key_value"
			result_table_name = "cmdb_key_value"
		}
	}
}

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sa_pattern"><sa_pattern action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><ci_type>cmdb_ci_appl_generic</ci_type><cpattern_type>2</cpattern_type><description/><directory>false</directory><enforce_proc_classy>false</enforce_proc_classy><invoke_per_account>false</invoke_per_account><metadata_id>1ef51f3e1ba23950ed78dd3cdc4bcbcd</metadata_id><name>Load Balancers GCP</name><ndl>library {
	name = "Load Balancers GCP"
	id = "1ef51f3e1ba23950ed78dd3cdc4bcbcd"
	description = "Load Balancers GCP"
	step {
		name = "LoadBalancer Api Call"
		custom_operation {
			attributes {
				attribute {
					name = "url"
					value = concat {
						"https://www.googleapis.com/compute/"
						get_attr {"API_version"}
						"/projects/"
						get_attr {"cloud_account_id"}
						"/aggregated/forwardingRules"
					}
				}
				attribute {
					name = "method"
					value = "GET"
				}
				attribute {
					name = "body"
					value = ""
				}
				attribute {
					name = "headers"
					value = ""
				}
				attribute {
					name = "formatted"
					value = "true"
				}
				attribute {
					name = "arrayName"
					value = "load_balancer_response"
				}
			}
			sys_id_op = "a6e5288173b363008c51d6dcb7f6a75e"
			to_var_names = "SystemVariable"
			parsing_strategy = empty_strategy {}
			if_not_found_do = nop {}
			is_paginated = 0
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Filter Api"
		if {
			condition = is_not_empty {get_attr {"load_balancer_response"}}
			on_true = custom_operation {
				attributes {
					attribute {
						name = "source"
						value = "load_balancer_response"
					}
					attribute {
						name = "source_column"
						value = ""
					}
					attribute {
						name = "table_name"
						value = "load_balancer"
					}
					attribute {
						name = "target_columns"
						value = "name:items.*.forwardingRules.name,object_id:items.*.forwardingRules.id,category:items.*.forwardingRules.region"
					}
				}
				sys_id_op = "eb6ef2e353a533003e76ddeeff7b124d"
				to_var_names = "SystemVariable"
				parsing_strategy = empty_strategy {}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				is_paginated = 0
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse LoadBalancer Table"
		transform {
			src_table_name = "load_balancer"
			target_table_name = "load_balancer"
			operation {
				set_field {
					field_name = "name"
					value = get_attr {"load_balancer[].name"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "object_id"
					value = get_attr {"load_balancer[].object_id"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "category"
					value = eval {"javascript: var getRegion = ${load_balancer[].category};
var region = getRegion.lastIndexOf('/');
if(region!==-1){
var rtrn = getRegion.substring(region + 1);
}
rtrn;"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "resource_type"
					value = "compute.v1.forwardingRule"
				}
			}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Move into cmdb_ci_cmp_resource table"
		union {
			table1_name = "load_balancer"
			table2_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
			result_table_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse Tags"
		set_attr {
			"tmp"
			eval {"javascript: var ArrayList = Packages.java.util.ArrayList;
var HashMap = Packages.java.util.HashMap;
// Create the target table
var loadBalancerLabels = new ArrayList();
// Iterate over the response table
var response = CTX.getAttribute(\"load_balancer_response\");
var responseIter = response.iterator();
while (responseIter.hasNext()) {
  var line = responseIter.next();
  var loadBalancersObj = JSON.parse(line);
  for (var loadBalancerIdx in loadBalancersObj.items) {
    var loadBalancer = loadBalancersObj.items[loadBalancerIdx];
    if (loadBalancer.hasOwnProperty(\"warning\")) {
      // if it has a property called \"warning\" then it doesn't exist
      continue;
    }
    for (i = 0; i < loadBalancer.forwardingRules.length; i++) {
      // Iterate over labels
      if (!loadBalancer.forwardingRules[i].labels) {
        continue;
      }
      for (var key in loadBalancer.forwardingRules[i].labels) {
        // Create new row in the target object
        var loadBalancerRow = new HashMap();
        loadBalancerRow.put(\"configuration_item\", loadBalancer.forwardingRules[i].id);
        loadBalancerRow.put(\"key\", key);
        loadBalancerRow.put(\"value\", loadBalancer.forwardingRules[i].labels[key]);
        loadBalancerLabels.add(loadBalancerRow);
      }
    }
  }
}
CTX.setAttribute(\"load_balancer_labels\",loadBalancerLabels);
rtrn = \"success\";
"}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Move into cmdb_key_value_table"
		union {
			table1_name = "load_balancer_labels"
			table2_name = "cmdb_key_value"
			result_table_name = "cmdb_key_value"
		}
	}
}

var regionIndex = getRegion.lastIndexOf('/');

			table1_name = "cloud_function_labels"
			table2_name = "cmdb_key_value"
			result_table_name = "cmdb_key_value"
		}
	}
}

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sa_pattern"><sa_pattern action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><ci_type>cmdb_ci_appl_generic</ci_type><cpattern_type>2</cpattern_type><description/><directory>false</directory><enforce_proc_classy>false</enforce_proc_classy><invoke_per_account>false</invoke_per_account><metadata_id>b75993361be23950ed78dd3cdc4bcbab</metadata_id><name>Pub Sub Topics</name><ndl>library {
	name = "Pub Sub Topics"
	id = "b75993361be23950ed78dd3cdc4bcbab"
	description = "null"
	step {
		name = "PUB-SUB API Call"
		custom_operation {
			attributes {
				attribute {
					name = "url"
					value = concat {
						"https://pubsub.googleapis.com/v1/projects/"
						get_attr {"cmdb_ci_cloud_service_account[*].account_id"}
						"/topics"
					}
				}
				attribute {
					name = "method"
					value = "GET"
				}
				attribute {
					name = "body"
					value = ""
				}
				attribute {
					name = "headers"
					value = ""
				}
				attribute {
					name = "formatted"
					value = "true"
				}
				attribute {
					name = "arrayName"
					value = "topics_response"
				}
			}
			sys_id_op = "a6e5288173b363008c51d6dcb7f6a75e"
			to_var_names = "SystemVariable"
			parsing_strategy = empty_strategy {}
			if_not_found_do = nop {}
			is_paginated = 0
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse API Call"
		if {
			condition = is_not_empty {get_attr {"topics_response"}}
			on_true = custom_operation {
				attributes {
					attribute {
						name = "source"
						value = "topics_response"
					}
					attribute {
						name = "source_column"
						value = ""
					}
					attribute {
						name = "table_name"
						value = "topics_table"
					}
					attribute {
						name = "target_columns"
						value = "name:topics.name"
					}
				}
				sys_id_op = "eb6ef2e353a533003e76ddeeff7b124d"
				to_var_names = "SystemVariable"
				parsing_strategy = empty_strategy {}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				is_paginated = 0
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse PUB-SUB"
		transform {
			src_table_name = "topics_table"
			target_table_name = "topics_table"
			operation {
				set_field {
					field_name = "object_id"
					value = get_attr {"topics_table[].name"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "category"
					value = get_attr {"cloud_account_id"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "name"
					value = eval {"javascript: var getName = ${topics_table[].name};var nameIndex = getName.lastIndexOf('/');if(nameIndex!==-1){var rtrn = getName.substring(nameIndex + 1);}rtrn;"}
				}
				set_field {
					field_name = "resource_type"
					value = "pubsub.v1.topic"
				}
			}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Put into cmdb_ci_cmp_resource Table"
		union {
			table1_name = "topics_table"
			table2_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
			result_table_name = "cmdb_ci_cmp_resource"
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Parse Tags"
		set_attr {
			"tmp"
			eval {"javascript: var ArrayList = Packages.java.util.ArrayList;
var HashMap = Packages.java.util.HashMap;

// Create the target table
var topicsLabels = new ArrayList();
// Iterate over the response table
var response = CTX.getAttribute('topics_response');
var responseIter = response.iterator();

while (responseIter.hasNext()) {  
   var line = responseIter.next();
   var topicsObj = JSON.parse(line);
   for (var topicsIdx in topicsObj.topics) {
      var topics = topicsObj.topics[topicsIdx];
      // Iterate over labels
      if (!topics.labels)
         continue;
      
      for (var key in topics.labels) {
	        // Create new row in the target object
          var topicsRow = new HashMap();
          topicsRow.put('configuration_item',topics.name);
          topicsRow.put('key',key);
          topicsRow.put('value',topics.labels[key]);
          topicsLabels.add(topicsRow);
      }
   }
}
CTX.setAttribute('topics_labels', topicsLabels);
rtrn = 'success'"}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "Move into Key Value Table"
		union {
			table1_name = "topics_labels"
			table2_name = "cmdb_key_value"
			result_table_name = "cmdb_key_value"
		}
	}
}
